<section name="389">
	<p><random dice="1"/> to see what you find amid the offerings.</p>
	<outcomes>
		<outcome range="1,2">
			<weapon name="Shadar spear" bonus="2"/> and a
			<tool name="flute" ability="charisma" bonus="1"/>
		</outcome>
		<outcome range="3,4">
			<armour name="plate armour" bonus="5"/> and a
			<item name="wolf pelt"/>
		</outcome>
		<outcome range="5,6">
			<item name="faery mead"/> and a
			<tool name="silver holy symbol" ability="sanctity" bonus="2"/>
		</outcome>
	</outcomes>
	<p>
		However, you have desecrated the shrine of Tambu, and have incurred his wrath. <lose ability="scouting" amount="1">Lose one point of SCOUTING</lose> permanently. Now <goto section="118"/>.
	</p>
</section>
